                        <h1 class="article-headline">Building DKU: From a decade of obstacles to its first undergraduate class</h1>
                                                <aside class="author">
                                
                                
                                                                            By
                                                                                                                                                                                                                    <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/bre-bradham">Bre Bradham</a>
