            <div class="col-8 col-md-8">
                
                <h1 class="headline has-photo"><a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/article/2019/02/is-duke-interdisciplinary-a-look-into-data-on-double-majors">Is Duke interdisciplinary? A look into data on double majors</a></h1>

                                    <span class="dateline has-photo">

                            
    
                                    
